    <briefdescription>
<para>Interface for trait lifecycle callbacks. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implement this interface on a BaseObject subclass to receive lifecycle notifications when the object is attached to or detached from a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> via <ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1IntegrationView_1ac6d7880f8e26b384f5ac14a22eacfe5d" kindref="member">IntegrationView::SetTrait()</ref>.</para>
<para>Objects stored as trait data that do NOT implement this interface will simply be stored without any lifecycle callbacks. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
